 Port Elizabeth - The 10111 Centre and the Community Service Centre at SAPS Mount Road are now operational. "Both facilities were closed on Friday, 19/06 due to a member having tested positive," the Nelson Mandela Bay Municipality advised residents. "The place has been decontaminated and the alternate operational venues are now closed. "SAPS management extends their appreciation to the communities for their understanding." Follow more RNEWS articles, subscribe to our YouTube channel and for breaking news LIKE us on Facebook. For news on the Western Cape click here. For great savings on life’s little pleasures visit Bargain Buys!  Know somebody who is getting married, Wedding and Function can assist.  Have kids, then you need to visit Kids Connection. Enjoy food and travel, then visit Home Food and Travel. Need assistance with an online presence, visit Agency One. 